snippet.title: 9 Classic Card And Board Games No. 2 - BBC Micro
snippet.description:
This is a complete playthrough of 9 Classic Card And Board Games No. 2 for the BBC Micro.
Review and scores in description.

Pros 
 +  A little more polished than the first game
 +  Controls are intuitive on most of the games

Cons
 -  Less well-known games than the first game


Score (out of 100)

 Controls   :=  42

Synopsis
9 more games each with better sounds and controls than part 1.
It would be good if I could play cribbage better.
